Northern Rock to Offer 90% Mortgages to Boost Revenue, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-02-28T01:42:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/northern-rock-to-offer-90-mortgages-to-boost-revenue-ft-says.html
Northern Rock Plc is planning to
provide home loans of up to 90 percent of the value of the
property as it seeks to increase its revenue in advance of its
return to private ownership, the Financial Times reported,
citing people familiar with the plans. The lender may begin
offering the new loans as early as today, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 